data.description: This lovely property offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. There’s 3 beds, 2 baths and 1 car garage.The home features a split floor plan with spacious living area, tile floors all throughout, kitchen and dining with stainless steel appliances. Large bedrooms. The Master bedroom has its own private bath. Home is equipped with hurricane shutters. Fully fenced backyard, perfect for outdoor activities and gatherings. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your forever home!
